      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in fair condition. It runs and drives, but has some mechanical issues that may require attention. The exterior shows visible wear including scratches and minor dents. The interior has noticeable wear as well. Suitable for a buyer comfortable with a vehicle that needs some work.",
      "price": 20000.0,
